window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b>Her curse didn’t end with a kiss. It awakened something darker.</b><br><br>Snow thought surviving the seven beasts who claimed her would break the spell.<br>She was wrong.<br><br>Now bound to their primal magic, she must navigate a forest full of secrets—and monsters who crave more than just her obedience.<br><br>Torn between the guardians who would die for her and the curse that demands more sacrifice, Snow must choose:<br><i>Submit to the beasts who claimed her… or unleash the one inside her.</i><br><br><b>Sins of Snow White: Bound to the Beasts</b> is Book 2 in a dark, spicy, standalone-friendly reverse harem fantasy romance series. Expect:<br>• Monster protectors with feral devotion<br>• Twisted fairytale tropes<br>• Emotional damage + primal tension<br>• High heat, zero shame<br><br><b>All characters 18+. No cliffhanger. Just claws, curses, and consequences.</b>"; 
